dmca.title: omniverse blog complains sumacumlaude hasn't earned its marks
dmca.body:
Attn: Blogger Legal Support DMCA complaints 
Infringement of Copyright Notice  

I have owned this blog 
http://omniverse.blogspot.com/ 
since 1-1-04, I have discovered that this blog 
http://www.sumacumlaude.blogspot.com/ 
is, as of when this letter is being written, an exact duplicate of my blog as it existed on 2-12-06, in other words that the owner thereof copied my exact template from my source code on that day; this material constitutes the entire content of that blog. 

Here are the answers to the questions your email to me of 3-15-06 said I need to answer to demonstrate that copyright infringement has taken place:
